task.summary: Created IPlayable interface with play method. Created Guitar class that implements IPlayable.
Created Piano class that implements IPlayable. It has various specific properties for Piano and getters for these.
Introduced new instrument package and moved instrument type classes into this package. IDE refactored other classes to reflect this new package.

Created abstract class Instrument which implements IPlayable interface.
Created InstrumentType ENUM for the category of instrument e.g. string, woodwind etc
Created ISell interface which specifies a calaculateMarkup method to be used with Items to work out the markup.

Created Item abstract class at the top of the hierarchy of stock items. This implements the ISell interface and the calculateMarkup method to return the markup based on the difference between retail and wholesale prices.
